      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\">\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>Here you can find projects which exemplify different new features within the XPU and RIS toolset.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"632\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647180/Cookies-N-Milk-docs.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433164801&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=632&amp;height=296\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544647180/Cookies-N-Milk-docs.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433164801&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"563\" data-width=\"1200\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544647248\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Cookies-N-Milk-docs.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544647180\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"80dd7e72-ac12-4182-80df-fd5c7d00b4ad\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647180/Cookies-N-Milk-docs.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433164801&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1200&amp;height=563 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647180/Cookies-N-Milk-docs.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433164801&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=632&amp;height=296 1x\"></span><p>Created by ar